- Use Bun as the package manager.
- Use Next.js 15 as the framework.
- Use Tailwind CSS for all styling.
- When implementing Server Actions, always handle errors and return a response in the following format: { success: boolean, error: string }- 
- Prefer using throwOnError when working with Supabase to simplify error handling.-
- Use lucide icon package.
- Use uncontrolled component for form. Prefer native html solution.
- Prefer type to interface for type declaration
